                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> the hadi mob bites and tears into the flesh of each enemy adjacent to the troop (@Check[type:reflex|dc:33|basic:true] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> [[/r (2d8+8)[slashing]]] damage plus hadi pestilence</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> [[/r (4d8+12)[slashing]]] damage plus hadi pestilence</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> [[/r (6d8+12)[slashing]]] damage plus hadi pestilence</p>"
